  <brief_title>Comparison of Glycemic Control Achieved With 2 Different Needles</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Glycemic Control Achieved With a 31 Gauge x 6 mm NovoFine® Needle vs. a BD 29 Gauge x 12.7 mm Ultra-Fine® Needle in Subjects With Diabetes Mellitus and a BMI Exceeding 30 kg/m2: An Open Label, Randomized, Two-Period Crossover Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
