  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in the United States of America (USA). The aim of this trial is to
      investigate if a 31 gauge x 6 mm needle will provide comparable blood glucose control to the
      29 gauge x 12.7 mm needle in obese subjects with diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
